				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Hy-Di/C%C3%B4ng-t%E1%BB%AD-h%C3%A0nh/poem-uM1JFB8xDqLpUKTHozrU_g">Công tử hành - 公子行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Hy-Di/author-sG1m4LG8HNG0zx1xauXNmA">Lưu Hy Di</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/D%E1%BA%A1-quy/poem-rCpLS4pHYsVrJjKIhfTnOg">Dạ quy - 夜歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-Tr%C3%BAc-oa/poem-nzlCqvE7hnaZoz79Koy3Lw">Đề Thạch Trúc oa - 題石竹窩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/H%C3%AD-v%E1%BA%A5n-Hoa-M%C3%B4n-t%E1%BB%ADu-gia-%C3%B4ng/poem-jX7In9BPlza4FJ_OhMhjhw">Hí vấn Hoa Môn tửu gia ông - 戲問花門酒家翁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Ph%E1%BA%A7n/Khu%C3%AA-o%C3%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-104/poem-exS024QWyhTzephbto5f1g">Khuê oán kỳ 104 - 閨怨其一百四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Ph%E1%BA%A7n/author-Qr01DWDfzQiHc7bG-WU6cg">Tôn Phần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BA%A1c-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nghi-h%C3%A0nh/poem-8PForxfR8TfWULc6cqqAAw">Mạc tương nghi hành - 莫相疑行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Mai/Tr%C3%A1c-B%C3%BAt-phong/poem-qd_m-u-uCVQopnHfBFgACQ">Trác Bút phong - 卓筆峰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Mai/author-0wWyWXBTsjFesQNO4r2tUQ">Viên Mai</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Truy-th%C3%B9-c%E1%BB%91-Cao-Th%E1%BB%A5c-ch%C3%A2u-nh%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ki%E1%BA%BFn-k%C3%BD/poem-3sPbsnBdTJGLI6krevujEg">Truy thù cố Cao Thục châu nhân nhật kiến ký - 追酬故高蜀州人日見寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BB%B1-Nam-Khang-v%C3%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-T%C3%ADn-ho%C3%A0n-quy%E1%BB%83n-thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i/poem-2YZNqlcvqwLOxe36xP-K0Q">Tự Nam Khang vãng Quảng Tín hoàn quyển thuật hoài - 自南康往廣信完卷述懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-QwR8mfkWimm7tarlC84k4w">Lý Mộng Dương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Xuy-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-ajF-qs_S6kiw3yoVeDT14w">Xuy địch - 吹笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
